OL,3,C'It's not fair': Grandmother feels
OL,4,Ctrapped as lift broken for two weeks
OL,6,FElderly residents at a 57-flat
OL,7,Fretirement block in Sussex say they
OL,8,Ffeel trapped as the complex's lift has
OL,9,Fbeen broken for the past two weeks.
OL,11,FThose living at the four-storey
OL,12,FWaverley Court in St Leonard's on-Sea
OL,13,Fsay they only now go out when they
OL,14,Fhave to, with some residents stuck
OL,15,Fcompletely.
OL,17,FJean Wilde is in her 80s and says she
OL,18,Fcan only get out with difficulty, with
OL,19,Fsteps a constant struggle.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
