OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776949868
OL,3,C'It's not fair': Grandmother feels
OL,4,Ctrapped as lift broken for two weeks
OL,6,FShe's lived at Waverley Court, run by
OL,7,FHome Group, for 3 years and says this
OL,8,Fisn't the first time the lift has
OL,9,Fbroken.
OL,11,FShe added: "Every day. everybody ...
OL,12,Fasks if they've heard anything, and
OL,13,Fthey haven't and it isn't fair because
OL,14,Fwe've all paid quite a lot of money,
OL,15,Fground rent and that, and we can't get
OL,16,Fout.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
