OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776949868
OL,3,C'It's not fair': Grandmother feels
OL,4,Ctrapped as lift broken for two weeks
OL,6,F"I can (get out), but it's still a
OL,7,Fstruggle getting up the stairs. You go
OL,8,Fup one, and then (by the) time I get
OL,9,Fup the second one, I'm holding on to
OL,10,Fthe bar up there and waiting, because
OL,11,Fmy legs go.
OL,13,F"I can't do it all in one go."
OL,15,FThings are equally difficult for
OL,16,Ffellow resident Sylvia Everit.
OL,18,FShe said: "It really messed me right
OL,19,Fup because I'm not well anyway.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
