OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776949868
OL,3,C'It's not fair': Grandmother feels
OL,4,Ctrapped as lift broken for two weeks
OL,6,F"I've just lost my husband at
OL,7,FChristmas, and ... it's been horrible.
OL,9,F"My granddaughter took me shopping
OL,10,Fyesterday and helped me up. But we
OL,11,Fdon't go out."
OL,13,FRuth Eagling, Homeownership Operations
OL,14,FManager at Home Group said: "We
OL,15,Funderstand how frustrating this issue
OL,16,Fwith the lift has been for our
OL,17,Fcustomers, and how long it has been
OL,18,Fout of service.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776949868
OL,3,C'It's not fair': Grandmother feels
OL,4,Ctrapped as lift broken for two weeks
OL,6,F"We had an emergency engineer attend
OL,7,Fwithin 45 minutes of the lift breaking
OL,8,Fdown, and they identified issues with
OL,9,Fsome of the electronic switches.
OL,11,F"Our lift contractor has had to source
OL,12,Fa specialist part to repair the lift,
OL,13,Fwhich is taking time. We have stressed
OL,14,Fto them the importance of getting this
OL,15,Frepair carried out as soon as
OL,16,Fpossible, and the impact that the
OL,17,Fdisruption is having on our customers.
OL,19,F"If any customer needs further
OL,20,Fassistance while the lift is out of
OL,21,Forder, please let our team know."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
